service.tut.pori.contentanalysistest

Class ContentAnalysisTestUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.contentanalysistest.ContentAnalysisTestUtils
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public final class ContentAnalysisTestUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    A collection of various test methods, and more or less everything not yet (or never will be) part of the official specification/implementation. One should NOT use these methods in any serious code.
